    <div class="prompt-footer">
      <div class="model-chips">
        <div class="mchip"><span class="mchip-dot c1"></span> Haiku</div>
        <div class="mchip"><span class="mchip-dot c2"></span> Llama</div>
        <div class="mchip"><span class="mchip-dot c3"></span> Mixtral</div>
        <div class="mchip"><span class="mchip-dot c4"></span> Gemma</div>
      </div>
      <button class="convene-btn">Convene the Council →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- DELIBERATING -->
<div class="section-title">— Deliberating —</div>
<div class="stream-grid">
  <div class="stream-card">
    <div class="sc-header">
      <span class="sc-name" style="color:#7c6ee0">Haiku</span>
      <div class="sc-status"><div class="status-ring ring-done"></div>Done</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sc-text">
      With only 3 paying customers, you lack enterprise proof points. PLG-to-enterprise transitions need 10+ customers + $5k ACV signal. <em>Stay PLG, raise price to $1k/mo first.</em>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="stream-card">
